                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>San Francisco</placeName>\n                                        <date>Dec. 15. 1852</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Revd Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Dear friend</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(5)\">I send you enclosed<lb/> Draft on <persName>Mess.\n                                                  M. Cauffman &amp; Co</persName>,\n                                                  <placeName>Phila.</placeName> Drawn by<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Roggenburger &amp; Co</persName>, for $24.00,\n                                        which I have collected for<lb/> the Occident, as per\n                                        enclosed statement; &amp; enclose you also<lb/> a fresh\n                                        subscription for the O.; had I more Time to<lb/> spare &amp;\n                                        our Californians would devote more Time in<lb/> reading your\n                                        intellectual work, I could, no Doubt have<lb/> sent you a\n                                        larger list of Subscription.</p>\n                              <p>I have recd your Letter, &amp; am sorry, that I cannot<lb/> comply\n                                        with your wishes for informing you, how<lb/> Jewish affairs\n                                        progress; however that much I can<lb/> tell you, that Jewish\n                                        Families are getting quite Numerous<lb/> in <placeName>San\n                                                  Francisco</placeName>, &amp; of late we had also\n                                        several Mar-<lb/>-riages taking place. The Jewish Population\n                                        all over<lb/>\n                                        <placeName>California</placeName> is very numerous, but our\n                                        Religion is<lb/> not by any means kept up in generality, as\n                                        it should be.<lb/> We have two Synagogues here, one Polish\n                                        &amp; one German,<lb/> which are open every\n                                        “<add>שבת</add>”, but are not very well attended,<lb/> &amp;\n                                        it is only on “<add>יום טוב</add>”, that you have the\n                                        opportunity of<lb/> witnessing the Synagogues crowded, where\n                                        there is generally<lb/> not Room enough to seat ½.</p>\n                              <p>It saves me some Trouble, <del>when</del> if I collect the\n                                        Subscriptions</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p30g3hj48/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
